Bnter,is,a,way,to,share,conversations,and,learn,more,about,the,lives,of,friends,and,others,Like,twitter,the,length,of,the,conversation,is,limited,so,the,most,meaningful,part,is,highlighted,The,Bnter,API,gives,users,access,to,practically,all,of,the,functionality,on,Bnter,Several,methods,are,provided,that,allow,interaction,with,both,users,and,their,conversations,The,API,uses,RESTful,protocol,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON